channel.title: Submit Bugs on Discord
channel.description:
Bugs are apparent mistakes that happen to **multiple people, not just you**
If you find a bug, please submit in the #bugs channel in the Discord server https://discord.gg/keyauth
If the issue doesn't happen to anyone but you, and it's on the default code example with **no changes**, then please create topic under this category https://community.keyauth.win/c/examples/5
